reviewText: A family favorite cartoon.  WIsh more episodes would be available.
Cute cartoon. Clean cartoons are hard to find. I like cartoons that I can watch with the kids and not have to worry about some of the comments or jokes.

I highly recommend this animated Christmas story to any one.  It is a perfect addition to your Christmas dvd collection.  My daughter absolutely loves it!  It is a sweet story with an adorable dog.  It is colorfu,l and the animation is great.

If you like dogs or puppies and the mischief they can get into
You will love What a Mess.
If you like Clifford, Garfield, Heathcliff, Marmaduke, or Belvedere(a very old cartoon) You will enoy this show
